## Phase 1 · ANALYZE (the gate decision)

**4-condition test (per task class)** — all four must pass:

| Task | 1. Repeats ≥weekly | 2. Auto verification | 3. Budget absorbs waste | 4. Senior-eng tools | Result |
|------|:---:|:---:|:---:|:---:|:---:|

**30-second check (per BUILD candidate)** — all five:

| Task | Weekly | Rejectable | Runnable | Hard stop | Human gate | Verdict |
|------|:---:|:---:|:---:|:---:|:---:|:---:|

**Candidate classification**

| Task | Verdict (BUILD / KEEP MANUAL) | If KEEP MANUAL: which box failed + remedy |
|------|---|---|

> If nothing qualifies: state "don't build a loop yet" + the shortest path to qualifying (usually: add automated verification). This is a successful outcome.

