## Phase 3 · HARDEN (sign-off — see references/03-failure-modes.md)

- [ ] Objective gate names a command + exit code
- [ ] Hard stop set (budget / iterations / time)
- [ ] Human approval gate before merge/deploy/deps/auth/payments
- [ ] Maker ≠ checker (different model; /goal checker ≠ maker)
- [ ] VISION.md restates non-negotiable constraints, reread each run
- [ ] Security gate: SAST + dependency audit + secret scanning
- [ ] No auto-install of unaudited skills/connectors
- [ ] Verbose logging off; logs sanitized
- [ ] Permission re-audit scheduled (≤30 days)
- [ ] Human owns reading diffs + spot-checking gates on a cadence

